spec_data.Name: libsearpc
spec_data.Description:
Searpc is a simple C language RPC framework based on GObject system. Searpc
handles the serialization/deserialization part of RPC, the transport part is
left to users.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 04 Aug 2017 01:14:57 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A simple and easy-to-use C language RPC framework
